                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "S'il se prêtait à la joie un moment.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "De vos malheurs je sais toute l'histoire ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "L'amour, l'hymen, ont trahi vos désirs :",
