                    "line_text": "Mais ne saurait altérer son repos.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Du cher objet que votre cœur adore",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Ne craignez rien ; comptez sur vos attraits :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
